SeedDM: Oven-dry mass of the seed, including seed wall

HeightMax: Rainforest Key, CSIRO permanent plots, Field observations
ReproAge: TFRC arboretum, Botanist and Landholder Interviews
Pollination_syndrome: Assigned by Dr. Dan Metcalfe, CSIRO, based on literature data and floral features.
SeedDM: CSIRO Fruit-Frugivore Interactions database, Metcalfe & Grubb (published and unpublished), RBG Kew seed database Liu et al (2008).  Data: 131 direct measurements, 76 inferred from seed or spore dimenssions.
